title: SPY 2013/14 SNOW PK - TREVOR
description:
Retro-inspired styling meets modern technology. The Trevor offers a comfortable blend of features and affordability to complement any style.

The Trevor is custom built from a flexible polyurethane frame and features an anti-fog cylindrical dual-lens system with anti-scratch protection, triple-layer Isotron™ face foam with moisture-wicking Dri-Force™ fleece, silicone-ribbed strap, 100% UV protection, is available with SPY's Flight™ Strap and is helmet compatible with the most popular helmets on the planet.
